    "popupContent": "<h2 class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">USOP&nbsp;Ha&nbsp;Long&nbsp;Bay&nbsp;Ultimate&nbsp;Series</span></h2><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The&nbsp;InterContinental&nbsp;Ha&nbsp;Long&nbsp;Bay&nbsp;Resort</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;pinnacle&nbsp;of&nbsp;luxury&nbsp;and&nbsp;elegance,&nbsp;perfectly&nbsp;situated&nbsp;along&nbsp;the&nbsp;stunning&nbsp;shores&nbsp;of&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Ha&nbsp;Long&nbsp;Bay</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">.&nbsp;This&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">five-star&nbsp;resort</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;offers&nbsp;world-class&nbsp;accommodations,&nbsp;exquisite&nbsp;dining&nbsp;options,&nbsp;and&nbsp;exceptional&nbsp;facilities&nbsp;designed&nbsp;to&nbsp;cater&nbsp;to&nbsp;every&nbsp;guest’s&nbsp;comfort&nbsp;and&nbsp;sophistication.&nbsp;With&nbsp;breathtaking&nbsp;views&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;bay’s&nbsp;emerald&nbsp;waters&nbsp;and&nbsp;limestone&nbsp;karsts,&nbsp;each&nbsp;room&nbsp;and&nbsp;suite&nbsp;provides&nbsp;a&nbsp;serene&nbsp;retreat,&nbsp;while&nbsp;the&nbsp;resort’s&nbsp;impeccable&nbsp;service&nbsp;ensures&nbsp;an&nbsp;unforgettable&nbsp;stay.&nbsp;Combining&nbsp;modern&nbsp;luxury&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;natural&nbsp;beauty&nbsp;of&nbsp;one&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;world’s&nbsp;most&nbsp;iconic&nbsp;destinations,&nbsp;InterContinental&nbsp;Ha&nbsp;Long&nbsp;Bay&nbsp;Resort&nbsp;sets&nbsp;the&nbsp;perfect&nbsp;stage&nbsp;for&nbsp;both&nbsp;relaxation&nbsp;and&nbsp;high-stakes&nbsp;poker&nbsp;action.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: r